text.tspan: Mental health and substance use disorders death rate by age, World
Estimated annual number of deaths by age group from mental health and substance use disorders per 100,000
people in the same age group. These include alcohol use, drug use, and eating disorders. Figures do not include
deaths resultant from suicide, which in some cases are related to these disorders.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease
